-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\n	mso-font-kerning:1.0pt;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜二＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">拟定计划</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">根据营<span style=\"color:black\">销科</span>传送的信息拟定配送计划，发出配送通知。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜三＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">做好送货准备</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">准备所需车辆，明确送货目的地。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜四＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">配货</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">集货：配货员将各个用户所需要的各种物品，按需要的品种、规格、数量，从仓库的各个货位拣选并集中起来；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">分拣：分拣员将集货形成的集中物品按运输车辆分开，分别堆放到指定的装卸点；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">配装：配货员将各个用户所需的各种物品、和车辆的装载容量组配起来。装卸工将客户所需的各种货物，以就近原则，按配送车辆的装载容量进行装载组配。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜五＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">送货</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">接营<span style=\"color:black\">销科</span>送货通知单，做送货准备；确认货物种类和数量；需要车辆的大小和数量；运送目的地；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">查看出库单和送货费用缴费单，装货；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">送至目的地。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">二、操作办法<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\"> </span></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜一＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">合同及票据管理</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">合同签订：《运输合同》（见附件一）必须在货物装车前签订；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">票据管理：严格程序、一票多联、核对无误、签字确认，具体见《货物托运单》（附件二）。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜二＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">装卸货管理</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">安全搬运，合理放置；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">装货、卸货及启封开箱时须双方验证。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜三＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆管理</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆有配送部统一管理，由专职司机负责驾驶；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆的各种证件必须齐全；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆必须定期或及时检修；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">严禁货运车辆超限、超载。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜四＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">运输货物管理</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">选择最佳运输路线，未经许可禁止改道；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">对非全密封车厢要做好防雨、冰、雪等措施；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">运输期间未经托运方同意禁止开启封条。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">三、协议签订</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\r\n0pt\">按照</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">《<b>货物运输合同》执行</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://www.mushw.com/uploads/货物运输合同.doc\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><b>附件：货物运输合同.doc</b></span></a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', '1', '', '1', 'ueelife', '2013-03-13 11:01:19', '', '2013-03-18 22:41:44', null);
INSERT INTO mu_article VALUES ('656', '前置现货通', null, '0', '103', '109', '仓储金融科负责《前置现货通业务流程及操作规范》的制定和修改，并对实施情况进行监督。仓储金融科主管领导对前置现货通业务流程及操作规范进行总体控制，仓储金融科具体执行本办法。', '<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>ZH-CN</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:SpaceForUL/>\r\n   <w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth/>\r\n   <w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone/>\r\n   <w:ULTrailSpace/>\r\n   <w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn/>\r\n   <w:AdjustLineHeightInTable/>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n   <w:SplitPgBreakAndParaMark/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignCellWithSp/>\r\n   <w:DontBreakConstrainedForcedTables/>\r\n   <w:DontVertAlignInTxbx/>\r\n   <w:Word11KerningPairs/>\r\n   <w:CachedColBalance/>\r\n   <w:UseFELayout/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n  <m:mathPr>\r\n   <m:mathFont m:val=\"Cambria Math\"/>\r\n   <m:brkBin m:val=\"before\"/>\r\n   <m:brkBinSub m:val=\"--\"/>\r\n   <m:smallFrac m:val=\"off\"/>\r\n   <m:dispDef/>\r\n   <m:lMargin m:val=\"0\"/>\r\n   <m:rMargin m:val=\"0\"/>\r\n   <m:defJc m:val=\"centerGroup\"/>\r\n   <m:wrapIndent m:val=\"1440\"/>\r\n   <m:intLim m:val=\"subSup\"/>\r\n   <m:naryLim m:val=\"undOvr\"/>\r\n  </m:mathPr></w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n<p class=\"NewNewNewNewNew\" style=\"line-height:200%\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体\">目的：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:#0400\">规范</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:black;mso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-ansi-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:#0400\">业务流程及操作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">适用范围：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN\">本办法适用于</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">业务</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN\">的管理与操作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">职责：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">仓储金融科负责《</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">业务流程及操作规范》的制定和修改，并对实施情况进行监督。仓储金融科主管领导对</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nmso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">业务流程及操作规范进行总体控制，仓储金融科具体执行本办法。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">＜一＞业务流程</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">客户和拟购货物经四方<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>银行、贸易公司、担保公司、仓储公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>认可；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">客户与贸易公司签订《委托采购协议》；贸易公司与供货方签订《购销合同</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">》，客户在银行存入其购货物一定比例的采购资金；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n16.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">客户存入采购资金后，根据《委托采购协议》和《购销合同》，就货款资金缺口部分提</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">交借款申请；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">贸易公司按照贷款金额的<span lang=\"EN-US\">50%</span>在银行存入过程保证金，此款项由银行予以冻结；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">经银行审批后，与客户签订手续，担保公司提供担保；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">银行放款至客户账户，并先于冻结；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">7.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">客户与贸易公司确定提货日期后，共同签署《用款申请》，经银行审核后，先将款项转入贸易公司专用账号，由贸易公司按《购销合同》转入供货方账号；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">8.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">客户、贸易公司、担保公司共同提货、检验，直至货物到达仓储公司仓库；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">9.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">开具仓单，由贸易公司将仓单通过背书方式，将货物交付客户；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">10.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">客户将货物质押给银行，变成现货通；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">11.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">偿还贷款，银行发放解除质押通知书，提货；</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">\r\n	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black\">12.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:black\">程序结束。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">＜二＞操作办法</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">按照</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">《前置现货通实施细则》操作</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\r\nlayout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">附件：</span></b><a href=\"http://www.mushw.com/uploads/前置现货通.doc\">前置现货通.doc</a></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" DefUnhideWhenUsed=\"true\"\r\n  DefSemiHidden=\"true\" DefQFormat=\"false\" DefPriority=\"99\"\r\n  LatentStyleCount=\"267\">\r\n  <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"0\" SemiHidden=\"false\"\r\n   UnhideWhenUsed=\"false\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"Normal\"/>\r\n  <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"9\" SemiHidden=\"false\"\r\n   UnhideWhenUsed=\"false\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"heading 1\"/>\r\n  <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"9\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"heading 2\"/>\r\n  